<div class="tsingle" style="float:left;margin:1px;width:128px;max-width:128px">
<div class="thumbimage"><a href="/wiki/File:Anthony_Mackie_by_Gage_Skidmore.jpg" class="image"><img alt="" src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/f/f8/Anthony_Mackie_by_Gage_Skidmore.jpg/126px-Anthony_Mackie_by_Gage_Skidmore.jpg" width="126" height="156" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/f/f8/Anthony_Mackie_by_Gage_Skidmore.jpg/189px-Anthony_Mackie_by_Gage_Skidmore.jpg 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/f/f8/Anthony_Mackie_by_Gage_Skidmore.jpg/252px-Anthony_Mackie_by_Gage_Skidmore.jpg 2x" data-file-width="2352" data-file-height="2916" /></a></div>
<div class="thumbcaption" style="clear:left"><a href="/wiki/Anthony_Mackie" title="Anthony Mackie">Anthony Mackie</a></div>
