<div class="tsingle" style="float:left;margin:1px;width:122px;max-width:122px">
<div class="thumbimage"><a href="/wiki/File:Brian_Geraghty_by_David_Shankbone.jpg" class="image"><img alt="" src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/0/08/Brian_Geraghty_by_David_Shankbone.jpg/120px-Brian_Geraghty_by_David_Shankbone.jpg" width="120" height="156" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/0/08/Brian_Geraghty_by_David_Shankbone.jpg/180px-Brian_Geraghty_by_David_Shankbone.jpg 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/0/08/Brian_Geraghty_by_David_Shankbone.jpg/240px-Brian_Geraghty_by_David_Shankbone.jpg 2x" data-file-width="1531" data-file-height="1985" /></a></div>
