</div>
<ul>
<li><i><a href="/wiki/Nine_From_Aberdeen" title="Nine From Aberdeen" class="mw-redirect">Nine From Aberdeen</a></i>, a 2012 book by <a href="/w/index.php?title=Jeffrey_M._Leatherwood&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Jeffrey M. Leatherwood (page does not exist)">Jeffrey M. Leatherwood</a> on the WWII forerunners of EOD, with an afterword by CSM James H. Clifford, military consultant for <i>The Hurt Locker</i>.</li>
</ul>
